---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About & Contact - The Golden Spoon">
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-12">About The Golden Spoon</h1>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="mb-4">Welcome to The Golden Spoon, where culinary excellence meets a warm and inviting atmosphere. Established in 2023, our restaurant was founded with a passion for exquisite food and unforgettable dining experiences. We believe that every meal should be a celebration, a moment to savor and share.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Our chefs are dedicated to crafting dishes that delight the senses, using only the freshest, locally sourced ingredients whenever possible. From classic comfort food to innovative culinary creations, our menu is designed to offer something special for every palate.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">At The Golden Spoon, we pride ourselves on our exceptional service and our commitment to creating a memorable visit for each guest. Whether you're joining us for a casual lunch, a romantic dinner, or a special occasion, we strive to make your time with us truly golden.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing The Golden Spoon. We look forward to serving you!</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-12">Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="mb-4">We're always happy to hear from you. Whether you have a question, a suggestion, or want to make a reservation, feel free to reach out.</p>
        <p class="mb-4"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">+1 (234) 567-890</a></p>
        <p class="mb-4"><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Restaurant Lane, Food City, FC 98765</p>
        <p>For reservations, please call us during our opening hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
